# 📧 Group Email Summarizer — AI Automation

An NLP-powered dashboard that reads email group threads and produces a clean summary with action items, owners, follow-up dates, and topic insights.

**Stack:** Python · sumy · nltk · Streamlit · Pandas

---

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
email-summarizer-ai/
│
├── app.py                   ← Main pipeline (run this first)
├── requirements.txt         ← Python dependencies
│
├── config/
│   └── config.py            ← Settings and file paths
│
├── services/
│   ├── email_reader.py      ← Reads emails from CSV dataset
│   ├── summarizer.py        ← NLP summarization using sumy
│   └── extractor.py         ← Extracts topic/actions/owner using nltk
│
├── dashboard/
│   └── dashboard.py         ← Streamlit dashboard
│
├── utils/
│   └── helper.py            ← Text cleaning utilities
│
├── data/
│   ├── emails.csv           ← Input email dataset
│   └── email_summary.csv    ← Auto-generated output
│
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Setup

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install pandas streamlit sumy nltk
```

### 2. Download nltk data
```bash
python -m nltk.downloader punkt punkt_tab averaged_perceptron_tagger
```

---

## 🚀 Running the App

### Step 1 — Run the pipeline
```bash
python app.py
```

### Step 2 — Launch the dashboard
```bash
streamlit run dashboard/dashboard.py
```

Opens at: http://localhost:8501

---

## 🔄 Workflow

```
Email Dataset (CSV)
       ↓
email_reader.py  →  Read & parse emails
       ↓
summarizer.py    →  NLP summarization (sumy LSA)
       ↓
extractor.py     →  Extract topic, actions, owner (nltk)
       ↓
data/email_summary.csv
       ↓
dashboard.py     →  Streamlit Dashboard
```

---

## 🖥️ Dashboard Features

| Tab | Features |
|---|---|
| 📋 Summary Table | Email Thread · Key Topic · Action Items · Owner · Priority |
| 🧵 Thread Details | Expandable cards per thread with full analysis |
| 📊 Insights | Priority chart · Owner chart · Topic tags |

